Privacy Policy for Halalmatic Kip

Introduction

Welcome to Halalmatic Kip! Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our mobile application ("App").

Data Collection and Use

We are pleased to inform you that Halalmatic Kip does not collect, use, or share any personal data or information from its users. This means:

No Personal Information Collection: We do not collect any personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, or any other identifiable information.

No Usage Data Collection: We do not track or collect any usage data, including but not limited to your interactions with the App, the features you use, or the time you spend on the App.

No Location Data: We do not access or collect any location data from your device.

No Device Information: We do not collect any information about your device, such as the model, operating system, or unique device identifiers.

Third-Party Services

Halalmatic Kip does not use any third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. Since we do not collect any data, there is no data to share with third parties.

Children's Privacy

Our App does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. As we do not collect any information, there is no risk of unintentional data collection from minors.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy
